FBIS4-40010 "drsov113_f_94025" FBIS-SOV-94-113 Daily Report 11 Jun 1994 National Affairs Leak Confined Within Station Leak Confined Within Station LD1106154494 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1325 GMT 11 Jun 94 LD1106154494 Moscow INTERFAX English BFN [Text] At the Chernobyl nuclear power station, a leak from a pool with used fuel cassettes was detected on 11 June. As the Chief of Ukraine's National Committee for Emergencies Sergey Nazarenko has told INTERFAX, water did not spread outside the station grounds. In his words, polluted water has been reliably collected for special treatment. The situation at Chernobyl is said to have returned to normal.
